---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="How We Rank Schools — Methodology" description="How British Schools Asia ranks British curriculum schools across Asia.">
  <Header slot="header" />

  <section class="section">
    <div class="bsa-container">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <p class="label mb-4">Methodology</p>
        <h1 class="mb-8">How We Rank Schools</h1>

        <div class="space-y-6 font-body text-black/70 leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            Our research team maintains a ranked index of British curriculum schools across Asia. Rankings reflect a combination of fee positioning and editorial assessment.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl mt-10 mb-4 text-black">Fee-based scoring</h2>
          <p>
            Tuition fees are the primary ranking factor. Schools with higher fee levels typically invest more heavily in facilities, staffing, and academic programmes. Our team collects and verifies fee data across every school in the index.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl mt-10 mb-4 text-black">Editorial assessment</h2>
          <p>
            Fees alone do not tell the full story. Our editorial team reviews each school's reputation across a range of sources and applies adjustments where warranted. Schools with significant negative signals may receive a downward adjustment in the rankings.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl mt-10 mb-4 text-black">Editorial reviews</h2>
          <p>
            We publish editorial reviews for schools where we have sufficient information to form a view. Where our research is still underway, the school profile displays factual information only.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl mt-10 mb-4 text-black">What the index does not do</h2>
          <p>
            This is not a league table of exam results. Academic outcomes may be incorporated in future editions. No school can pay to be ranked, promoted, or removed.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl mt-10 mb-4 text-black">Currency</h2>
          <p>
            All fees are converted to USD for cross-country comparison. Local currency figures are shown alongside USD on every school profile.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-12">
          <a href="/rankings" class="btn-ghost-dark">View Rankings</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer slot="footer" />
</BaseLayout>
